2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper uses HOG features, which are commonly used in computer vision for object detection and image classification. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses machine learning algorithms and their application to face image recognition. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image encryption and compression, which are relevant to the field of multimedia.
